column8: R4_Decod_1a : TCP RST is invalid if there is no corresponding TCP ACK (tcp.flags == 16) before belonging to the same session containing correct seq_nb and ack_nb.
C4_Analyse_03h: The minimum size of an IP fragment is 28 bytes and for an IP fragment with offset 0 it is 40.
IP fragmentation : a fragment with a size less than 9 bytes (allowed but could be an evasion).
Overlapping IP fragmentation : difference in offset of concomitant fragments less than fragment length (allowed but could be an evasion).
